{"tid":2273083,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"以左膠之道還左膠之身","createTime":"2020-11-05T13:03:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-05T14:24:26.000Z","uid":59570,"like":3,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"a8241d4d752a05da22855d25d962b3b1168ab94e","tid":2273083,"uid":59570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T13:03:52.000Z","msg":"小妹英文唔好，但有啲提議睇下有冇國際戰線或者meme友整啲文宣<br />\n<br />\n美國反trump既有女權，blm呢類我地稱為左膠<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但其實係左膠心目中，「民主」既地位都好重<br />\n<br />\n可能佢地已經習以為常到忘記咗佢地支持既概念「女權，平權，大愛」呢啲概念其實都係建基於人權，而「人權」同「民主」可以話係不可分割<br />\n<br />\n我想帶出既邏輯係：<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">「民主黨舞弊到出哂面，如果投票比佢地既選民都唔出手糾正或反對拜登呢種行為，佢地係有份扼殺緊整個美國既核心價值，什至係扼殺緊佢地stand for 既概念（平權 etc.)」</span>"},{"pid":"6da28b1c8161f71129b69d9d88e6b4bb689dc712","tid":2273083,"uid":59570,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T13:05:12.000Z","msg":"有冇機會拉返美國左膠既理性返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04c855edebce6c9b1ea0c0609de66d296c16331b","tid":2273083,"uid":54223,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T13:05:52.000Z","msg":"左膠會選擇性失明"},{"pid":"03b96f98d0a6f90fa6c7db72f2c4565f52a8cd40","tid":2273083,"uid":44646,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T13:06:18.000Z","msg":"你不如睇下FOX有無報，點報你講既大規模舞弊，<br />\n再考慮是否出聲"},{"pid":"bc114519c1c3e9357c6a7f2e803df95cde242139","tid":2273083,"uid":23160,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6da28b1c8161f71129b69d9d88e6b4bb689dc712","tid":2273083,"uid":59570,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T13:05:12.000Z","msg":"有冇機會拉返美國左膠既理性返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T13:06:50.000Z","msg":"有理性就唔係膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n反侵反到賣國都撐<br />\n拉條撚"},{"pid":"7f3842245e201b072e2f66032a087ec18622ac9e","tid":2273083,"uid":154486,"